WEBVTT

00:02.108 --> 00:04.299
Drake is unbelievable.

00:04.596 --> 00:07.876
He's one of those guys who just gets away
with anything, you know.

00:08.581 --> 00:10.124
Time for a snack.

00:11.053 --> 00:15.347
He does whatever he wants and,
like never gets in touble.

00:16.125 --> 00:17.398
Cake is good.

00:18.372 --> 00:21.560
It's like he leads a charmed life.
Must be nice.

00:21.812 --> 00:25.567
Me, I always try to do the right thing.
- Milk.

00:26.328 --> 00:30.729
I follow all the rules. 'Cause if I even think
about doing something wrong..

00:30.842 --> 00:33.402
I get busted.
I don't get it.

00:36.129 --> 00:38.560
I wish I knew Drake's secret.

00:42.508 --> 00:45.610
Just once, I'd like to get away with something..

00:45.822 --> 00:47.809
Josh, get your feet off the coffee table!

00:49.014 --> 00:51.354
Every time!

00:59.996 --> 01:03.405
Where's Scottie's brother with the dune buggy?
- Calm down. He'll be here any minute.

01:03.410 --> 01:06.593
I can't wait! I've never
had a dune buggy before!

01:06.609 --> 01:08.705
We're gonna buggy it up!

01:12.208 --> 01:14.245
Hello. Trevor, where are you?
- Who is it?

01:14.375 --> 01:16.005
Scottie's brother.
- Where is he?

01:16.291 --> 01:18.009
You're lost?
- Lost?

01:18.099 --> 01:20.590
Okay, okay..
Where are you right now?

01:21.562 --> 01:23.506
look around and tell me what you see.

01:29.541 --> 01:31.915
... and I see some bushes,
and a tree..

01:32.851 --> 01:36.194
And a dog..
Boy dog

01:37.117 --> 01:39.676
And I see you.
- You're here.

01:41.497 --> 01:44.530
Where's the buggy?
- Open up the door.

01:47.949 --> 01:49.702
This is gonna be awesome.

01:49.885 --> 01:52.622
We can drive to the Zippy Mart whenever we want.

01:52.781 --> 01:55.422
We can drive girls to the Zippy Mart.
- Yes..

01:55.450 --> 02:00.314
'cause girls love convenience stores.
The buggy!

02:07.594 --> 02:09.209
That's it?

02:09.517 --> 02:12.371
What happened to it?
- You said it was in good shape.

02:12.410 --> 02:13.534
It is..

02:13.687 --> 02:15.299
You shoulda seen it before I fixed it up.

02:15.904 --> 02:18.767
Oh, now I'm all depressed.

02:18.864 --> 02:21.441
Wel-well, come on.
At least it runs..

02:23.153 --> 02:24.605
right?

02:24.650 --> 02:27.208
Oh yeah.
It runs.

02:27.236 --> 02:28.927
Cool!
Come on, Josh, jump in.

02:29.881 --> 02:32.519
Okay!
It's buggy time!

02:40.267 --> 02:42.050
You said it runs.

02:42.531 --> 02:45.515
Oh, you meant the dune buggy.

02:45.659 --> 02:47.762
Yeah, no..
That-that's broken.

02:48.992 --> 02:50.135
See ya.

02:53.050 --> 02:55.706
It's not buggy time..

02:56.185 --> 02:58.762
It's dead buggy time.

